<h2>Bubble Sort Algorithm</h2>
<p>Bubble sort is a simple sorting algorithm that repeatedly steps through the list...</p>

<h3>Pseudocode:</h3>
<pre>
for i from 1 to n:
    for j from 1 to n - i:
        if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:
            swap(arr[j], arr[j + 1])
</pre>

<h3>Code Implementation (Python):</h3>
<pre>
def bubble_sort(arr):
    n = len(arr)
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(0, n-i-1):
            if arr[j] > arr[j+1]:
                arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1], arr[j]
</pre>
